sources: ['US20010023249A1', '(S)-Azepane-1-carboxylic acid (1-{4-[[4-(1-hydroxy-cyclohexylethynyl)-phenyl]-(3-methyl-but-2-enyl)-amino]-piperidine-1-carbonyl}-3-methyl-butyl)-amide', '0760', '(S)-Azepane-1-carboxylic acid (1-{4-[(4-iodo-phenyl)-(3-methyl-but-2-enyl)-amino]-piperidine-1-carbonyl}-3-methyl-butyl)-amide (0.50 g, 0.49 mmol) was dissolved in THF (4 mL), treated with triethylamine (0.34 mL, 2.45 mmol), 1-ethynyl-1-cyclohexanol (94 RL, 0.74 mmol), Pd(Ph3P)2Cl2 (34 mg, 0.049 mmol), and cuprous iodide (4.8 mg, 0.028 mmol). The reaction was stirred overnight at room temperature, then heated to 40째 C. overnight. Another 1.5 equivalents of the acetylene, 0.1 equivalents of Pd(Ph3P)2Cl2, and 0.05 equivalents of cuprous iodide were added and the reaction was heated to 40째 C. overnight. The reaction was then concentrated in vacuo and chromatographed on silica gel eluting with 4:3 hexane/EtOAc to give 116 mg (39%) of the desired product.']
